<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB00054</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT INSTITUTING INCLUSIVE EDUCATION, ESTABLISHING INCLUSIVE EDUCATION LEARNING RESOURCE CENTERS FOR CHILDREN AND YOUTH WITH SPECIAL NEEDS (CYSNs) IN ALL PUBLIC SCHOOLS DIVISIONS, PROVIDING FOR STANDARDS AND GUIDELINES, AND APPROPRIATING FUNDS THEREFOR</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : "Inclusive Education For Children And Youth With Special Needs Act"
Seeks to improve the quality of existing programs for gifted and talented pupils and create learning centers catering specifically for children and youth with special needs. Ensures that economically disadvantaged pupils be provided with full participation in these unique opportunities. </td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>CABOCHAN, MANUEL III. D.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2019-07-01</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Tambunting (000 2019-08-06)</td><td>2. Suntay (000 2019-09-12)</td><tr><td>3. Ong (R.) (000 2019-11-18)</td><td>4. Tiangco (000 2019-11-18)</td><tr><td>5. Nieto (000 2020-02-19)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON BASIC EDUCATION AND CULTURE ON 2019-07-23</td></tr></table>